Yellow.ai provides a comprehensive development suite designed to bridge the gap between business users and technical developers.

1.6.1 The AI Agent Builder: No-Code/Low-Code
The core tool is the ""AI Agent Builder,"" a No-Code/Low-Code environment. It features ""Agentic Generation,"" where users can build agents using natural language prompts. A user simply types, ""Build an agent that helps customers track flights and book upgrades,"" and the platform automatically generates the necessary intents, flows, and tool definitions. This democratizes AI development, allowing subject matter experts (SMEs) to create functional agents without writing code.   

1.6.2 Developer Collaboration and Legacy Integration
