The platform specifically addresses the ""Integration Barrier"" with ""Generative Integration."" Developers can paste raw API documentation (Swagger, OpenAPI, or even a CURL command) into the builder, and the system automatically generates the integration code, data mapping, and error handling logic. This capability significantly accelerates the connection to legacy backend systems, which is often the bottleneck in enterprise deployments.   
