1.12.1 Versioning and Rollback
The platform includes a robust ALM suite designed for enterprise CI/CD workflows. It supports distinct environments (Development, Staging, Production) with version control for every agent component. The ""One-Click Rollback"" feature allows administrators to instantly revert an agent to a previous stable state if a new deployment shows anomalies in production.   

1.12.2 Granular Promotion
Deployment is not ""all-or-nothing."" The system enables ""Granular Promotion,"" allowing developers to push updates to specific modules (e.g., updating the ""Returns"" flow) without redeploying or risking the stability of the ""Sales"" flow. This modularity is essential for large enterprises where different teams may own different parts of the customer journey."																					
