1.15.1 Architecture and Uptime
Yellow.ai guarantees 99.99% Uptime for enterprise customers. The platform is built on a Kubernetes-based microservices architecture, deployed across multiple Availability Zones (AZs) in the cloud (AWS preferred). This architecture ensures high availability and fault tolerance. The system is designed to auto-scale horizontally to handle massive spikes in demand (""Burstable Capacity""), supporting billions of conversations quarterly for global Fortune 500 clients.   

1.15.2 SLA Management
The platform includes built-in SLA Management tools. Administrators can define Service Level Agreements for various metrics (e.g., First Response Time < 30s, Resolution Time < 5 mins). The system monitors these in real-time and triggers alerts or automated escalations if a ticket is approaching an SLA breach, ensuring compliance with contractual obligations. "																					
