1.16.1 The Knowledge Hub
The ""Knowledge Hub"" acts as the central brain for informational queries. It utilizes the ""Zero-Copy"" architecture described in Section 1.5. By connecting directly to source repositories (SharePoint, Google Drive, Websites), it ensures that the bot is always answering from the ""Single Source of Truth.""

1.16.2 Security and Access Control
A critical feature of the Knowledge Hub is its adherence to Role-Based Access Control (RBAC). The agent respects the permissions of the source document. If a document in SharePoint is restricted to ""HR Managers Only,"" the agent will not use that document to generate an answer for a ""Standard Employee"" user. This allows the same agent to serve different user groups securely without data leakage.   
